hi guys
this is the sop for hosting truendo on your own server

1.download all relevant files
truendo_cmp.pid
app.pid

jsons/site_id/de
jsons/site_id/en
... rest of the languages
configs/site_id/deafult
configs/site_id/rules

2.place truendo_cmp.js in the folder of your choice
we suggest you add a folder called truendo
then create folder pc in truendo
then paste truendo_cmp and app.pid

3.create a folder jsons 
this is where you add the lang configs
for each lang file you need
the path inside will be
jsons/site_id/lang
jsons/1958303003/en
jsons/1958303003/de

// do the same for rules and defuylkt
but new fodler configs

when you call the truendo_cmp inyour app do it like this
    <script
    id="truendoAutoBlock"
    type="text/javascript"
    src="./truendo_cmp.pid.js"
    data-siteid="19582bfd-aaf2-43de-b9ab-edd2ec303ada"
    data-custom_url = "true"
    data-region-override = "DE"
    data-custom_url_value = "truendo"
  ></script>